sentences.sentence: Transform the dimensional physical data model to Cubing model.
sentences.translation: 将多维物理数据模型转换为Cubing模型。

sentences.sentence: Cubing Services provide multidimensional access to your relational data.
sentences.translation: Cubing Services提供对关系数据的多维度访问。

sentences.sentence: So you need to add cube to the Cubing model before it can be deployed.
sentences.translation: 因此，您需要将多维数据集添加到Cubing模型中，然后才可以对其进行部署。
